properties.Title: Land Recovery Landfill
properties.Description: Privately owned by Waste Connections Inc. with 21,588,591 tons of waste in place. Opened in 1999 and will close in 2032.

properties.Title: Cedar Hills Regional Landfill
properties.Description: Publicly owned with 43,806,272 tons of waste in place. Opened in 1965 and will close in 2046.

properties.Title: Roosevelt Regional MSW Landfill
properties.Description: Privately owned by Republic Services Inc. with 120,944,152 tons of waste in place. It handles about 70% of household waste in Washington State and is the 4th largest lanfill in the United States. Opened in 1990 and will close in 2085.

properties.Title: Terrace Heights Landfill
properties.Description: Publicly owned with 6,966,909 tons of waste in place. Opened in 1974 and will close in 2030.

properties.Title: Hidden Valley Landfill
properties.Description: Privately owned by Waste Connectins Inc. with 17,325,280 tons of waste in place. Opened in 1965 and closed in 1998.

properties.Title: Cowlitz County Headquarters Landfill
properties.Description: Publicly owned with 10,398,414 tons of waste in place. Opened in 1993 and will close in 2120.

properties.Title: Ephrata Landfill
properties.Description: Publicly owned with 2,787,559 tons of waste in place. Opened in 1942 and will close in 2034

properties.Title: Greater Wenatchee Landfill
properties.Description: Privately owned by Waste Management with 6,644,627 tons of waste in place. Opened in 1972 and will close in 2113.
